      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf08439-task`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Map to Canonical Schema",
